, and show that the\nresulting spectrum provides a good match to observed WNL stars, strongly\nsuggesting that the physical mechanisms we have identified are the ultimate\ncause of the WNL phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 17 Jul 2019 17:59:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Mar 2020 16:28:57 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 2 May 2020 23:02:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-05"}
