a property holds only if the electromagnetic\nenergy-momentum tensor is divergence-free. For the Minkowski tensor this\ncondition is satisfied, whereas for the Abraham tensor it is not.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 18 Jul 2019 08:54:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-19"}
